    accepts $2a$ prefix
  - 6 failed attempts triggered 30-min rate limit
Fix:
  - Generated $2a$ bcrypt hash for test1234, updated testuser
  - Recreated admin (ADMIN rank) and testuser2 (USER rank) in DB
  - Cleared rate limit entries from game_risk_incidents
  - Restarted server to reload AccountCache + reset rate limiter
